      "side": 1,
      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues - Must fix before merge] Line 80: When showOriginal is enabled, OriginalBody is returned directly and bypasses the existing MessagesAdapter.parseMessage path used for Body. If that parser sanitizes/normalizes rich text, links, emojis, or previews, the original message can render inconsistently and may expose unsanitized user-controlled text. Route the selected body through the same parsing/rendering path instead of returning OriginalBody raw, or explicitly force plain text for this branch.\n```suggestion\nconst displayBody \u003d showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite ? OriginalBody : Body;\nif (displayBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 ParsedBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0) {\n    MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(Id, displayBody, UtilsAdapter.getAppValue(Settings.DisplayHyperlinkPreviews), rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n    return \"\";\n}\n```",
